# FORMATTING

# Maintain LF (Unix-style) newlines in text files.
*   text=auto eol=lf

# Make sure various media files never get somehow auto-detected as text
# and then newline-converted.
*.gif binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.eot binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.svg binary
*.ttf binary
*.png binary
*.otf binary
*.tif binary
*.ogg binary
*.bson binary
*.bmp binary
*.mp3 binary
*.pdf binary